overview:
TryMunity is a social community website for the brain injury survivors, TBI Survivors, medical and social supporters, their friends and families. It’s completely non-commercial and offers a private, protected way to find, share, distribute and communicate with others who share your interests and experiences.

TryMunity is a committed non-commercial community of brain injury survivors, TBI Survivors, medical and social supporters, their friends and family members. It is determined to provide a private, secure way to find and communicate with others members who share your interests and experiences. Through this platform, TBI survivor and supporters share their lives, stories, and resources during life changing events. It is a perfect traumatic brain injury network that extends brain injury support for the survivors and their families.

The social brain injury network invites people who have been suffered from a Traumatic Brain Injury, cancer, heart attack…and more. The purpose of the TryMunity is peer support.
